n Irish Chart |publisher=IRMA |access-date=July 17, 2013 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090602061251/http://www.irishcharts.ie/search/placement |archive-date=June 2, 2009 |df=mdy-all }} Only results when searching \"I heard it through the grapevine\"</ref>\n|align=\"center\"|7\n|-\n{{singlechart|Dutch40|25|artist=Marvin Gaye|song=I Heard It Through The Grapevine}}\n|-\n|South African Chart<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.rock.co.za/files/springbok_top_20_(G).html |title= I heard it through the grapevine in South African Chart |author= John Samson |accessdate= July 17, 2013}}</ref>\n|align=\"center\"|3\n|-\n|UK ([[Official Charts Company]])<ref name=\"UK\">{{cite web|url= http://www.officialcharts.com/artist/_/marvin%20gaye/ |title= Marvin Gaye |publisher= Official Charts Company |accessdate= July 17, 2013}}</ref>\n|align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n|US [[Billboard Hot 100|''Billboard'' Hot 100]]<ref name=\"awards\">{{cite web|url= http://www.allmusic.com/artist/marvin-gaye-mn0000316834/awards |title= Marvin Gaye awards on Allmusic |work= Allmusic |publisher= Rovi Corporation |accessdate= July 17, 2013}}</ref>\n|align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n|US ''Billboard'' [[Hot R&B/Hip-Hop Songs|Hot R&B Singles]]<ref name=\"awards\"/>\n|align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n|US ''[[Cashbox (magazine)|Cash Box]]'' Top 100<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tropicalglen.com/Archives/60s_files/19690118.html|title=Cash Box Top 100 1/18/69|publisher=|access-date=December 8, 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220105953/http://tropicalglen.com/Archives/60s_files/19690118.html|archive-date=December 20, 2016|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n|align=\"center\"|1\n|}\n;(Reissue version)\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n!Chart (1986)\n!Peak<br/>position\n|-\n{{singlechart|Flanders|18|artist=Marvin Gaye|song=I Heard It Through The Grapevine}}\n|-\n|[[Irish Singles Chart]]<ref name=\"IRL\"/>\n|align=\"center\"|4\n|-\n{{singlechart|Dutch40|18|artist=Marvin Gaye|song=I Heard It Through The Grapevine}